This paper is primarily focused on video action recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a new module (Gate-Shift Module) that improves the efficiency of spatio-temporal feature extraction, which could be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
